@csrfToken = naR9gc8Z-Z3exoJxWLJvQ2k-AkDLr5hGdRkM
### Get CSRF Token
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/auth/csrf-token

### Signup
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json
X-CSRF-Token: {{csrfToken}}

{
    "firstName": "Abdullah",
    "lastName": "Odulate",
    "userName": "abdullahodulate",
    "email": "abdulluhodulate@gmail.com",
    "password": "password123"
}

### Verify Email
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/auth/verify-email
Content-Type: application/json
X-CSRF-Token: {{csrfToken}}

{
    "email": "abdulluhodulate@gmail.com",
    "otp": "4654"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json
X-CSRF-Token: {{csrfToken}}

{
    "email": "abdulluhodulate@gmail.com",
    "password": "password123"
}

### Refresh Token
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/auth/refresh


