### Create Property
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/properties
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-CSRF-Token: {{csrfToken}}

{
    "title": "Luxury Penthouse in Lagos",
    "description": "A stunning 4-bedroom penthouse with ocean views and modern amenities.",
    "price": 500000,
    "type": "APARTMENT",
    "status": "AVAILABLE",
    "bedrooms": 4,
    "bathrooms": 5,
    "featured": true,
    "location": {
        "address": "123 Ocean View Drive",
        "city": "Lagos",
        "state": "Lagos",
        "country": "Nigeria",
        "latitude": 6.4527,
        "longitude": 3.3892
    }
}

### Get All Properties
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/properties
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Get Property by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/properties/{{propertyId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Update Property
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/v1/properties/{{propertyId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-CSRF-Token: {{csrfToken}}

{
    "price": 550000,
    "status": "PENDING"
}

### Delete Property
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/v1/properties/{{propertyId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-CSRF-Token: {{csrfToken}}

